title: Nvidia’s $200 Jetson Orin Nano minicomputer is 80 times faster than the previous version
description: Nvidia has just expanded its system-on-module family with the addition of the Jetson Orin Nano. It will deliver up to 80x the performance of its predecessor.

title: Nvidia ‘GeForce Beyond’: live coverage of RTX 4090 launch and more
description: Nvidia's GeForce Beyond event starts today as part of GTC 2022, where the company is expected to announce the RTX 4090.

title: Spellcheckers in Google Chrome could expose your passwords
description: Are you using an enhanced version of spellchecker in Microsoft Edge or Google Chrome? Bad news -- your personal information might be at risk.
